title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 27 2022
description:
Biden White House slams Atlanta Braves nickname on day the team visited the White House. Montage of Biden's past racist statements. NH Senate Candidate Don Bolduc, a former police officer and retired United States Army brigadier general, joins Clay and Buck to make the case against his opponent Maggie Hassan. Former special forces caller tells Clay & Buck why General Bolduc is a legend. C&B cover the senate races.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
